### Create x-layout visualization!

Quick start in the browser without a line of code!
[Open App](https://heatgraphy.streamlit.app)

[Read Documentation](https://heatgraphy.readthedocs.io/en/stable)


### Installation

```shell
pip install heatgraphy
```

